title: Looking for a ADC Main to duo with, A good one ...

embed.description: Create & discover new Champion builds/strategies, check your Summoner statistics and try our powerful LoL charts.

body:
Looking for a good adc to duo with, trying to find someone that has a brain and is a decent player. I want to starting grinding to diamond so a kinda high elo player please. Would be even better if you can also teach me some stuff to improve my game.

Please if you're bronze,silver or gold don't add me. No offence but i want to win more then 80% of my games.

IGN: Kat To Plat  (send me a message right away or you will get deleted, To many adds sorry)

replies.body: you're and offence* :3, i'm a supp main. Good luck finding someone to play with.
Thank you, My spelling is not to good.
Lol, What ever you say buddy. Tho my border does say other wise.
